                            <comment id="111877" author="thomasd" created="Thu, 22 Jan 2015 06:29:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Petar,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;do you have a concrete example at hand for what you want to simplify?&lt;/p&gt;

